    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026130/extras/a48ac57af2cdb08f085434e9e340fad7.poster.avif?t=1725114249\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026130/extras/a48ac57af2cdb08f085434e9e340fad7.webm?t=1725114249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026130/extras/a48ac57af2cdb08f085434e9e340fad7.mp4?t=1725114249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Cathy And The Others</strong> 是一款情感丰富的叙事游戏，让你代入 Cathy 的角色，她在一间陌生房子的卧室里醒来。探索、寻找，但最重要的是… <strong>逃脱</strong>！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>沉浸式叙事</strong>: Cathy And The Others 提供独特且实验性的叙事体验。揭开 Cathy 的过去，了解她发生了什么事！<br></li><li><strong>基于谜题的探索</strong>: 在逃脱室风格中找到解锁下一个房间的方法。<br></li><li><strong>互动环境</strong>: 与房子中的各种物品互动，帮助你逃脱、阅读笔记并找到秘密组合。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>多重结局</strong>: 为自己做出最佳选择。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026130/extras/200363674589834b3bffc4c66e9f185e.poster.avif?t=1725114249\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026130/extras/200363674589834b3bffc4c66e9f185e.webm?t=1725114249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026130/extras/200363674589834b3bffc4c66e9f185e.mp4?t=1725114249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul></li></ul></li></ul>",
